@@mEGOMANCER@@W

Egomancers bend force of will into weaponized cognition. They do not overpower
through brute spell volume, but through pressure, disruption, and focused mindfire.

@@mPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wRemort non-physical damage@@W bonus
    (+0.5% per level, up to +50% at 100).
  * @@wPsionic-recovery healing@@W scales with Egomancer remort levels
    (+2% per level, up to +200% at 100 on that healing line).

@@mUnique Egomancer mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wEgomancer stance@@W (dual-cast / no-hit caster posture).
  * Primary remort bridge into mental-pressure Kinetimancer play.
  * Uses @@wIntelligence@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@mEgomancer reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wNecromancer + Egomancer remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wEquip Wand@@W permanently.

